org.sakaiproject.genericdao.api.mappers
Interface StatementMapper

All Superinterfaces:
DataMapper
public interface StatementMapper
extends DataMapper

Allows defining of SQL to use when executing standard queries, ? will be replaced by the values to be updated or inserted in standard SQL fashion

Author:
Aaron Zeckoski (azeckoski@gmail.com)

Method Detail

getInsertTemplate

String getInsertTemplate()
Returns:
the template to use when generating insert statements, use the TABLE_NAME, COLUMNS and VALUES constants to indicate replacements OR return null to use the default templates

getSelectTemplate

String getSelectTemplate()
Returns:
the template to use when generating selects, use the SELECT, TABLE_NAME, and WHERE constants to indicate replacements OR return null to use the default templates

getUpdateTemplate

String getUpdateTemplate()
Returns:
the template to use when generating updates, use the TABLE_NAME, UPDATE and WHERE constants to indicate replacements OR return null to use the default templates

getDeleteTemplate

String getDeleteTemplate()
Returns:
the template to use when generating deletes, use the TABLE_NAME and WHERE constants to indicate replacements OR return null to use the default templates
